{
  "info": {
    "name": "Whatfix Discussion API",
    "_postman_id": "whatfix-discussion-api-v1",
    "description": "Production-grade Express.js messaging API. All endpoints return JSON.\n\n**Base URL**: `http://localhost:3000`\n\n**Error format**:\n```json\n{ \"error\": { \"status\": 422, \"message\": \"Validation failed\", \"details\": [...] } }\n```\n\n**Edge cases covered**:\n- 409 on duplicate email\n- 422 on missing/invalid fields\n- 404 on unknown IDs\n- 422 on backward status transitions\n- Idempotent message sends via `clientRequestId`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:3000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "userId", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "userId2", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "messageId", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "GET /health",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/health", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["health"] }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Users",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create user (happy path)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status is 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "pm.test('Returns user with id', () => {",
                  "  const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "  pm.expect(body.data.id).to.be.a('string');",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', body.data.id);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Alice\",\n  \"email\": \"alice@example.com\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "users"] }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Create second user (for messages)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status is 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('userId2', pm.response.json().data.id);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Bob\",\n  \"email\": \"bob@example.com\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/users", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "users"] }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Create user — 422 missing name",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status is 422', () => pm.response.to.have.status(422));",
